ck-bands-for-the-next-generation/| dead-url = yes}}</ref>。2010年，美國雜誌《[[Consequence_of_Sound|Consequence of Sound]]》將X JAPAN列入「全球十五大最受樂迷崇拜的樂團」<ref>{{cite web| language = en| title = List ‘Em Carefully: The Top 15 Cult Acts| work = [[Consequence_of_Sound|Consequence of Sound]]| url = http://consequenceofsound.net/2011/11/list-em-carefully-the-top-15-cult-acts/| date = 2011-11-30| accessdate = 2013-04-20| archive-date = 2013-05-10| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130510205922/http://consequenceofsound.net/2011/11/list-em-carefully-the-top-15-cult-acts/| dead-url = no}}</ref>。2012年4月，他們贏得《{{link-en|左輪手槍 (雜誌)|Revolver (magazine)|左輪手槍}}》雜誌的「年度最佳國際樂團獎」<ref name="xjapanmusic"/><ref name="Loudwire">{{cite web| language=en| title=X Japan Take Home ‘Best International Band’ Award at Golden Gods| work=loudwire.com| url=http://loudwire.com/x-japan-take-home-best-international-band-award-at-golden-gods/| accessdate=2012-05-15| archive-date=2012-05-15| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120515212325/http://loudwire.com/x-japan-take-home-best-international-band-award-at-golden-gods/| dead-url=no}}</ref>。2013年1月17日，獲得{{link-en|Loudwire音樂獎|Loudwire Music Awards}}的「最忠實粉絲獎」<ref name="most devoted">{{cite web| language=en| title=X Japan Win Most Devoted Fans in the 2012 Loudwire Music Awards| work=loudwire.com| url=http://loudwire.com/x-japan-most-devoted-fans-2012-loudwire-music-awards/| accessdate=2013-01-17| archive-date=2013-01-18| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130118014313/http://loudwire.com/x-japan-most-devoted-fans-2012-loudwire-music-awards/| dead-url=no}}</ref>，2015年2月3日，再獲提名入圍。

此外，X JAPAN也在日本音樂產業之外擁有崇高地位。1999年，在[[日本國政府|日本政府]]的請託下，YOSHIKI為[[日本皇室|日本皇室]]創作歌曲，並在「{{link-ja|慶祝天皇陛下即位十周年國民慶典|天皇陛下御即位十年をお祝いする国民祭典}}」上彈奏了奉祝曲〈Anniversary〉<ref name="WashYoshiki">{{cite news|language=en|title=Yoshiki seeks global rock glory for X Japan|url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2011/03/08/AR2011030806491.html|work=[[華盛頓郵報|華盛頓郵報]]|date=2011-03-08|accessdate=2013-03-02|first=Yuri|last=Kageyama|archive-date=2016-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305022149/http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2011/03/08/AR2011030806491.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web| language = en| title = Nimaime wa so-so, baby| work = [[日本時報|日本時報]]| url = http://www.japantimes.co.jp/culture/2002/02/13/music/nimaime-wa-so-so-baby/#.UXxK3cpArIV| date = 2002-02-13| accessdate = 2013-04-27| archive-date = 2014-02-20| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140220170326/http://www.japantimes.co.jp/culture/2002/02/13/music/nimaime-wa-so-so-baby/#.UXxK3cpArIV| dead-url = no}}</ref>。日本前[[日本內閣總理大臣|首相]][[小泉純一郎|小泉純一郎]]是X JAPAN的著名樂迷之一<ref name="WashYoshiki"/><ref name="JapanZone">{{cite web|language=en|title=Koizumi Junichiro|url=http://www.japan-zone.com/modern/koizumi_junichiro.shtml|work=Japan-Zone.com|accessdate=2013-03-02|archive-date=2013-02-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130203022926/http://www.japan-zone.com/modern/koizumi_junichiro.shtml|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|language=en|title=Japanese PM's son seeks limelight|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/entertainment/1468352.stm|work=[[英國廣播公司新聞|英國廣播公司新聞]]|date=2001-08-01|accessdate=2013-03-02|archive-date=2013-12-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131202222247/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/entertainment/1468352.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。小泉所屬[[自由民主黨_(日本)|自民黨]]，曾多次使用X JAPAN的歌曲〈FOREVER LOVE〉，作為國政選舉廣告的音樂，小泉最終也順利當選<ref>{{cite web|language=en|title=LDP unveils new TV commercials, poster featuring Koizumi|url=http://www.thefreelibrary.com/LDP+unveils+new+TV+commercials,